Install phpHiveAdmin on cleanly CentOS linux system
1. Download phpHiveAdmin and decompress the zip
2. Run "chmod +x install_centos(x).sh" ( Choose compatible shell script with you operation system, support centos 5 or 6 now )
3. Run "./install_centos(x).sh"
4. Open config.inc.phpï¼Œchange hive_thrift_host and hive_thrift_port
Change hadoop_home, hive_home, java_home to their installed path
5. Open browser and visit http://your_ip. (Not support IE6)